1
00:00:12,760 --> 00:00:13,440
Ms. Wang.

2
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:17,840
Do you know

3
00:00:18,240 --> 00:00:19,170
these two women?

4
00:00:21,040 --> 00:00:22,700
I saw them once at the wedding.

5
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:24,200
If I remember correctly,

6
00:00:24,280 --> 00:00:26,540
they were Xu Xing's college classmates.

7
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:29,720
Just that one time?

8
00:00:30,560 --> 00:00:31,160
Officer,

9
00:00:31,240 --> 00:00:32,700
I know what you want to ask.

10
00:00:33,160 --> 00:00:34,040
I also know

11
00:00:34,280 --> 00:00:35,280
Xu Xing might be having an affair

12
00:00:35,280 --> 00:00:37,000
with one of them,

13
00:00:37,280 --> 00:00:38,360
or maybe both.

14
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:39,960
It doesn't matter.

15
00:00:39,960 --> 00:00:40,690
I don't care.

16
00:00:41,280 --> 00:00:42,760
Ours is a business marriage.

17
00:00:42,760 --> 00:00:44,400
There's absolutely no affection.

18
00:00:44,400 --> 00:00:47,000
We've been doing our own things from the start.

19
00:00:47,280 --> 00:00:49,000
I have no interest in dealing with

20
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:50,600
the messes he makes outside.

21
00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:51,720
Ms. Wang,

22
00:00:52,520 --> 00:00:53,520
we invited you here

23
00:00:53,520 --> 00:00:54,780
not because of Xu Xing,

24
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:56,560
but because of Zhao Wenbing.

25
00:00:58,680 --> 00:01:00,280
In Li Xiaoru's phone,

26
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:03,140
we found evidence of your affair with Zhao Wenbing,

27
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:07,530
and evidence of you two conspiring to transfer assets from Xu Xing's company.

28
00:01:07,760 --> 00:01:09,090
Could you explain this?

29
00:01:11,520 --> 00:01:13,180
You knew Lin Ran was pregnant,

30
00:01:13,480 --> 00:01:15,800
so you instigated Li Xiaoru to kill her.

31
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:19,740
Then you ordered Zhao Wenbing to kill Li Xiaoru.

32
00:01:20,880 --> 00:01:22,410
Do I have any reason to kill?

33
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:23,320
That's right.

34
00:01:23,520 --> 00:01:24,960
I cheated with Zhao Wenbing,

35
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:27,220
but I'm not afraid of Xu Xing finding out.

36
00:01:27,720 --> 00:01:29,000
You say I killed people.

37
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:30,320
Do you have evidence?

38
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:32,320
Without evidence, it's slander.

39
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:33,800
Please don't get agitated.

40
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:34,680
We are just

41
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,320
making a hypothesis.

42
00:01:35,320 --> 00:01:36,320
I can't calm down.

43
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:38,400
You just said Lin Ran was pregnant.

44
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:39,660
It's Xu Xing's, right?

45
00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:41,680
And that Li Xiaoru.

46
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:44,130
I know she is Xu Xing's ex-girlfriend,

47
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:47,520
and I know she's been entangled with him all along.

48
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:48,920
But I'm the victim,

49
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:51,160
yet you suspect I'm the murderer.

50
00:01:52,440 --> 00:01:54,680
If you think there are any other suspects,

51
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:56,039
you can provide them to the police,

52
00:01:56,039 --> 00:01:57,900
and we will verify them one by one.

53
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,600
If there's any similar questioning,

54
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:01,040
I'll have a lawyer present.

55
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:02,640
Without my lawyer,

56
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:04,160
I won't say another word.

57
00:02:05,440 --> 00:02:05,970
Alright.

58
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:08,180
We respect your decision.

59
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:12,330
Chief Zhang.

60
00:02:13,040 --> 00:02:13,970
Li Xiaoru's case

61
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:15,920
is very likely related to Zhao Wenbing,

62
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:17,120
Xu Xing, and Wang Min.

63
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:18,880
So I want to apply as soon as possible

64
00:02:18,880 --> 00:02:20,480
to track the communication records of the three of them

65
00:02:20,480 --> 00:02:21,880
and find a breakthrough.

66
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:23,680
I can approve it.

67
00:02:23,920 --> 00:02:24,450
However,

68
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:27,200
you are familiar with Xu Xing's identity and background.

69
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:29,040
There are certain risks in investigating him.

70
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:29,520
So,

71
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:31,640
you need to solve the case as soon as possible.

72
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:32,170
Besides,

73
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:33,600
I heard from Xiao Zhai

74
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:35,930
that these cases might be serial murders.

75
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:36,960
How is it going?

76
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,640
Have you found the mastermind?

77
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:39,170
Who is it?

78
00:02:39,720 --> 00:02:40,720
Is it just one person?

79
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:41,640
Not confirmed yet.

80
00:02:41,640 --> 00:02:43,240
We are still investigating.

81
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:45,930
Once confirmed,

82
00:02:46,440 --> 00:02:48,240
you must report it immediately.

83
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,480
The impact of this incident

84
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:50,440
is no small matter.

85
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:51,170
Understood.

86
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:54,370
I'm leaving.

87
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:21,440
Zhao Wenbing.

88
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,280
Someone first encouraged

89
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:44,480
Li Xiaoru to kill Lin Ran,

90
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:49,060
then ruined my relationship with Xiaoru and forced me to kill her.

91
00:03:49,480 --> 00:03:51,740
It seems this person knows us inside out.

92
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:55,960
Could it be a college classmate who knows our relationship well?

93
00:03:59,040 --> 00:04:00,300
What are you busy with?

94
00:04:02,200 --> 00:04:02,840
Nothing.

95
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:05,240
Why did you dig these out?

96
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:08,480
Xu Xing is planning a class reunion.

97
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:08,720
Ah.

98
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:09,970
Here,

99
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:10,520
son.

100
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:11,730
Drink your milk.

101
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,140
It helps you sleep.

102
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:21,240
Mom.

103
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,440
I'm a bit lactose intolerant.

104
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:24,880
Buy lactose-free milk next time.

105
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:26,740
It's also better for you seniors.

106
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:27,360
Oh.

107
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,400
What intolerance?

108
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:31,080
You'll get used to it.

109
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:34,320
If you have so many rules,

110
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,210
hurry up and find a wife.

111
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:38,920
I've arranged a blind date for you tomorrow night.

112
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,520
Remember to leave some time.

113
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:44,680
But I have a work dinner tomorrow night.

114
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:46,010
I might be a little late.

115
00:04:46,080 --> 00:04:46,680
Cancel it.

116
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:48,840
Your current job is

117
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:50,360
just working for Xu Xing.

118
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:53,380
Marriage is the top priority.

119
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:53,880
Ah.

120
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:56,060
Got it, Dad.

121
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:57,840
I'll be there on time.

122
00:04:58,159 --> 00:04:58,800
Have a seat first.

123
00:04:58,800 --> 00:04:59,800
I'll go take a look.

124
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,130
Come.

125
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,720
Oh, you are really...

126
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,440
Must-play LARP of the year.

127
00:05:37,440 --> 00:05:38,480
Death Descends.

128
00:05:39,320 --> 00:05:41,320
The third villain to be judged.

129
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,600
Zhao Wenbing.

130
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:51,520
Master.

131
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,800
We found the fake maintenance worker.

132
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:54,600
You found him.

133
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,640
Where did you find him?

134
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:56,500
Chen found him.

135
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:01,980
How did you find him, Qiu Chen?

136
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:04,200
The electrical experts confirmed

137
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:05,130
that someone did

138
00:06:05,280 --> 00:06:07,080
tamper with the circuit system.

139
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:07,730
Also,

140
00:06:08,320 --> 00:06:10,920
the circuit system of that bathtub is very complicated.

141
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:13,200
It would be hard for a non-professional to do it.

142
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:13,600
Yeah.

143
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:16,240
I checked with the brand's company.

144
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:17,300
Someone indeed

145
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:19,320
the night before the incident,

146
00:06:19,320 --> 00:06:20,780
sneaked into their office

147
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:23,210
and stole the maintenance manual.

148
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,800
Although that person was very careful,

149
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:26,600
wearing a mask

150
00:06:26,640 --> 00:06:27,300
and gloves,

151
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:30,280
a piece of hair was left at the scene.

152
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:33,760
Wow.

153
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:36,659
You can even spot such short hair?

154
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,530
You should learn from Qiu Chen.

155
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:42,180
Is it Zhao Wenbing?

156
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:42,840
Yes.

157
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:44,280
I guess

158
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:46,170
he had two purposes.

159
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:47,120
First,

160
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:48,880
to clear his name.

161
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,560
Second,

162
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,840
to lead us

163
00:06:53,159 --> 00:06:54,120
to suspect

164
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:55,360
Xu Xing

165
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:56,530
and Wang Min.

166
00:06:58,920 --> 00:06:59,440
Oh.

167
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:01,840
This kid has such a high IQ to commit crimes.

168
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:04,940
This case is getting more and more interesting.

169
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:14,440
Whoa.

170
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,580
I don't drink cold drinks.

171
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:22,200
Just kidding.

172
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:24,160
Hahaha.

173
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:24,840
Not funny.

174
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:26,520
Thanks.

175
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,000
Oh, right.

176
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:30,720
Yeah.

177
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:32,520
Xu Xing said earlier

178
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:36,320
that the ways the characters died in the script

179
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,720
match up with Lin Ran

180
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:38,450
and Li Xiaoru

181
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:39,600
perfectly.

182
00:07:40,840 --> 00:07:42,480
But in that script,

183
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,800
Zhao Wenbing and then Xu Xing,

184
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:46,800
they both died too.

185
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:51,840
Are you saying the next one is Zhao Wenbing?

186
00:07:57,880 --> 00:07:58,280
Hello.

187
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:04,840
Sir, Cyber Security traced that the mysterious person

188
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:06,640
first sent Xu Xing the dirt on Zhao Wenbing.

189
00:08:06,640 --> 00:08:08,600
Then Zhao Wenbing also received a judgment message.

190
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,000
Now,

191
00:08:09,320 --> 00:08:11,980
the location of the message has been confirmed.

192
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:13,240
Zhao Wenbing is in danger.

193
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:14,170
I'll go find him.

194
00:08:14,440 --> 00:08:16,080
You go after the person checking the info.

195
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:16,920
Follow him.

196
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:17,370
Okay.

197
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:18,120
Stay sharp.

198
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:18,440
Yes.

199
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,520
Okay, I got it.

200
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:32,940
Lost him again.

201
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:39,880
At 7:30 a.m.,

202
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:43,400
he started from Jiangcheng University

203
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:45,490
and took us to the university town.

204
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:51,720
Then he led us to the old town.

205
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,740
He circled the old town twice,

206
00:08:56,640 --> 00:08:57,400
and took us

207
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,010
to the West Port.

208
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:03,840
Now he has led us to Ninghai Street.

209
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:10,840
The place he could go is

210
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:18,480
Chengxi Industrial Zone.

211
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:21,040
Zhao Wenbing's route is like a maze.

212
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:22,240
How did you deduce it?

213
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,040
Cut the crap.

214
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:23,770
Let's go now.

215
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:24,920
If we are a few minutes late,

216
00:09:24,920 --> 00:09:26,380
Zhao Wenbing will be dead.

217
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:27,520
Go.

218
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:28,330
Let's go.

219
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:40,340
Hey.

220
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,340
That's the guy.

221
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:44,720
Stop!

222
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:49,760
Stop!

223
00:09:59,920 --> 00:10:00,520
Don't run!

224
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:01,160
Stop!

225
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:26,920
Keep running.

226
00:10:27,920 --> 00:10:29,450
Aren't you good at running?

227
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:31,320
Take him away.

228
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:35,560
Name.

229
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:37,980
Huang Chen.

230
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:39,680
Age.

231
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:41,340
Twenty-three.

232
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:42,540
Come on,

233
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:43,880
tell me exactly

234
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:46,240
why you sent these kinds of text messages.

235
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:47,120
I was tricked.

236
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,400
Just a few days ago,

237
00:10:49,400 --> 00:10:50,330
someone added me

238
00:10:50,520 --> 00:10:52,380
and offered me two thousand yuan.

239
00:10:52,560 --> 00:10:53,520
I just had to go to an internet cafe

240
00:10:53,520 --> 00:10:55,520
and use a computer to send a message.

241
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:56,440
Go on.

242
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:59,440
I didn't even look at the content of the message.

243
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:01,570
I thought it was just a game promotion.

244
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:02,640
If that's all,

245
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,330
then why did you run?

246
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:06,040
Officer.

247
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:06,920
I'm not stupid.

248
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:09,730
Two thousand yuan just to send a few messages?

249
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:12,760
I also felt something fishy was going on.

250
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:14,980
But I didn't expect

251
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,640
you'd find me so quickly.

252
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:18,000
Be serious.

253
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:20,040
This is a murder case.

254
00:11:20,720 --> 00:11:21,120
What?

255
00:11:21,520 --> 00:11:22,120
Murder?

256
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:24,170
No, Officer,

257
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:26,040
I absolutely didn't kill anyone.

258
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:27,680
I don't even know those people.

259
00:11:27,680 --> 00:11:29,210
We just chatted a few times,

260
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:30,960
and it was all online.

261
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:32,640
You can check the internet cafe.

262
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:33,970
He just gave me the money

263
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:35,730
and then deleted me.

264
00:11:39,160 --> 00:11:39,960
Find it for me.

265
00:11:40,160 --> 00:11:40,760
Which one?

266
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:47,770
Th-this one.

267
00:11:50,040 --> 00:11:51,100
This Patrick Star?

268
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:51,570
Yeah.

269
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:54,040
Yuxiren.

270
00:11:56,280 --> 00:11:57,410
Zhao Wenbing's car.

271
00:11:57,560 --> 00:11:57,960
Hurry.

272
00:12:12,400 --> 00:12:12,930
This way.

273
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:17,640
Help!

274
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:20,760
Help!

275
00:12:23,560 --> 00:12:24,020
Police!

276
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:25,660
Save them quickly!

277
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:32,640
Go!

278
00:12:54,920 --> 00:12:55,920
Get out of the car.

279
00:13:03,640 --> 00:13:04,040
Get in.

280
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:07,480
Boss.

281
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:08,640
The matter is settled.

282
00:13:08,640 --> 00:13:09,520
We've beaten him,

283
00:13:09,520 --> 00:13:10,560
and tampered with the car.

284
00:13:10,560 --> 00:13:12,080
We left no trace.

285
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:13,200
Got it.

286
00:13:34,280 --> 00:13:35,680
It's Zhao Wenbing's car.

287
00:13:35,920 --> 00:13:36,250
Oh no!

288
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:37,450
It's on fire!

289
00:13:46,240 --> 00:13:46,900
Where is he?

290
00:13:48,040 --> 00:13:48,500
Master.

291
00:13:48,640 --> 00:13:49,100
Master.

292
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:52,120
Zhao Wenbing's car had an accident.

293
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:53,080
But he wasn't in the car.

294
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:54,120
He got out and ran away early on.

295
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:54,650
Ran away?

296
00:13:54,800 --> 00:13:55,160
Yes.

297
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:57,200
He escaped so fast.

298
00:13:57,800 --> 00:13:59,880
It seems Zhao Wenbing is extremely afraid of that person.

299
00:13:59,880 --> 00:14:00,200
Yes.

300
00:14:00,680 --> 00:14:02,440
I went to investigate Zhao Wenbing's car.

301
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:04,900
I found the fuel line had been tampered with.

302
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:06,650
What do you think, Qiu Chen?

303
00:14:07,040 --> 00:14:09,320
Have them continue hunting Zhao Wenbing in the city first.

304
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:11,360
I guess he still has unfinished business.

305
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,560
He won't leave today.

306
00:14:13,040 --> 00:14:14,840
Let's go check the auto repair shop.

307
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:15,370
Let's go.

308
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:19,600
I'd better tag along.

309
00:14:19,720 --> 00:14:20,180
No need.

310
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:21,400
Ah.

311
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:23,160
There is a problem with the fuel line.

312
00:14:23,160 --> 00:14:23,620
This...

313
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:24,970
That's impossible.

314
00:14:25,160 --> 00:14:26,680
Would the police come to you if there was no evidence?

315
00:14:26,680 --> 00:14:27,210
Hey, hey.

316
00:14:27,280 --> 00:14:28,120
Officer.

317
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:29,720
This has nothing to do with me.

318
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:31,320
I just fixed a seat for him that day.

319
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:31,840
As for the rest,

320
00:14:31,840 --> 00:14:33,200
I didn't touch anything.

321
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:36,460
We'll know if you touched it by checking the surveillance.

322
00:14:37,400 --> 00:14:37,800
Right.

323
00:14:38,160 --> 00:14:39,020
I remember now.

324
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:39,770
That day,

325
00:14:39,840 --> 00:14:41,300
when I was fixing his seat,

326
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:43,320
someone from my neighborhood's property management called me,

327
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:44,600
saying my house was on fire.

328
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:46,040
I left in a hurry,

329
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:47,600
and the door wasn't closed tightly.

330
00:14:47,600 --> 00:14:48,260
As a result,

331
00:14:48,400 --> 00:14:50,240
some bastard made a prank call to me,

332
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:51,680
saying my house wasn't on fire at all.

333
00:14:51,680 --> 00:14:51,940
Yes.

334
00:14:52,360 --> 00:14:53,360
Someone must have

335
00:14:53,520 --> 00:14:54,650
sneaked into my shop

336
00:14:54,760 --> 00:14:55,960
when I wasn't looking,

337
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:57,320
and tampered with his car.

338
00:14:57,320 --> 00:14:58,040
Where are the security cameras?

339
00:14:58,040 --> 00:14:58,280
Uh.

340
00:14:58,600 --> 00:14:59,600
Yes, we have them.

341
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:01,090
I have it on my phone.

342
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:09,940
*Sigh.*

343
00:15:10,520 --> 00:15:11,200
Officer.

344
00:15:11,480 --> 00:15:12,280
N-now,

345
00:15:12,640 --> 00:15:14,100
do you believe what I said?

346
00:15:18,520 --> 00:15:20,250
Make a copy of this video for me.

347
00:15:21,040 --> 00:15:22,480
I'll contact you later if needed.

348
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:22,680
Ah.

349
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:23,720
Okay, okay.

350
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:25,280
I'll copy it for you right now.

351
00:15:25,280 --> 00:15:26,080
Just a moment.

352
00:15:27,560 --> 00:15:30,420
Who do you think would mess with Zhao Wenbing's car?

353
00:15:31,920 --> 00:15:33,780
Besides that mysterious person,

354
00:15:33,840 --> 00:15:35,560
the people who most want him to have an accident

355
00:15:35,560 --> 00:15:36,560
are Xu Xing and Wang Min.
